These past 4 months have been crazzzzy! Haha I broke my foot, then floods, problems, life, blessings. So I moved! To a bigger place and then my birthday was yesterday! Haha 😂 oh everything all at once! 

My art show is on hold because well.... floods. But I have more space now to create! 

I'm also a guest lecturer tomorrow at the University of Vienna. Haha 😂 what is life!

Hope you're taking care of yourselves and working towards your goals and dreams. ✨
